headline.print_headline: Searchers Dismiss Possibility Wreckage in Bay of Bengal Is From MH370
headline.main: Searchers Dismiss Possibility Wreckage in Bay of Bengal Is From MH370

lead_paragraph: A private company said it had found what it believes is wreckage of a plane in the Bay of Bengal that should be investigated as potential debris from missing Malaysia Airlines Flight MH370, but the possibility was dismissed by search coordinators.
